 Quilldart ran towards the pod which was only a few feet away now. Proto 
stayed inbetween 3 and Quilldart. Quilldart transformed and cracked open the 
pod and slammed the Galvapred reprograming chip into it. If the pod couldnt 
find a animal to take shape as a demographic of an animal was put in the 
chip. (Ill let you decide what that will be.) Quilldart turned and saw many 
other bots close to the bod he fired shots at them all.
